" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n邱騰華指，香港對外經貿關係並非建基於個別團體的意見，而是基於互惠利的情況。他又指，假若將修例扯上營商環境及其他國家是「拉得太遠」。他亦指，政府有責任對修例的範圍及實際操作等方面作出闡釋及討論。他續指，希望有足夠時間讓政府官員能有機會在立法會法案委員會解釋修例建議，並讓立法會有足夠時間審議草案，並指這是立法會的責任。"},{"pid":"b5ef3d06b57b5a8eb40c7c8e3c48856ef26f2d41","tid":2155581,"uid":114463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:05:09.000Z","msg":"香港作為中國既一個城市點解要有特別代遇？<br />\n<br />\n而家中國製造好得罪你咩？作為林媽媽既手下你係咪鼓吹緊國家分裂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbf42d8ac525f447cfbb2c4726b93a624b8d4d1f","tid":2155581,"uid":62247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:05:23.000Z","msg":"佢精神分裂完未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b1e02857a3addceb78f64a66c45214d4c4ed02","tid":2155581,"uid":149494,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:07:32.000Z","msg":"邏輯混亂不堪<br />\n一黎你香港本身就小，唔存在會唔會以大欺小既問題，因為你本來就無咁既能力<br />\n二黎中國同香港政府不嬲強調一國大於兩制，將香港製造等同中國製造就係尊重一國大於兩制之表現<br />\n三黎美國在世貿就係有話事權，等於中國對世衛有話事權一樣，唔滿意既你可以唔玩，另起爐灶<br />\n<br />\n結論：作為一個月入超過三十萬既政府高官，講一堆廢話但又無幫助香港解決問題既能力，不如你辭職讓個位出黎比d後生仔做啦，你咁撚廢"},{"pid":"84688dab7a615aef1ff5ae55eb52adba304f1403","tid":2155581,"uid":154054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:08:34.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">邱騰華港獨<br />\n分裂國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持一個中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8740941cc090d347d74ff4fbf5053ac01eeab1f1","tid":2155581,"uid":1430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"632fe077607f5244d8a365e836ba0fdfd5b1b720","tid":2155581,"uid":300775,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:01:23.000Z","msg":"最撚自我陶醉果個咪係你自己囉鳩頭華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:12:24.000Z","msg":"個11個戰犯都一樣<br />\n永遠都係up美國無資產 唔嚮往美國 制裁無影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e5a13bced218abac619b481bc38cbd1ae92690","tid":2155581,"uid":29248,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:15:30.000Z","msg":"政府引狼入室連爆3波疫情，香港半年生意跌足8成，但地產霸權租金又唔見減8成。<br />\n<br />\n淨係死剩把口，乜7都做唔到，食屎啦你！！！！！"},{"pid":"6e175db66ad7d1e2f5b8e737bba0ad7d1d453a53","tid":2155581,"uid":95777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:15:37.000Z","msg":"你on9架 邱生?<br />\n香港係中國一部分咪made in china囉<br />\n係咪睇唔起中國製?"},{"pid":"c7adc23b3a837eab3260850403bbe9a69235dbff","tid":2155581,"uid":263213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:16:04.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"f4c448e6d5b128fb8a99f2c7c4c7f625adbb7296","tid":2155581,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:18:20.000Z","msg":"不如將條友講啲野做文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526cea4cd56f54e51012bd072484a5b25595f6cf","tid":2155581,"uid":11447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:19:08.000Z","msg":"收皮啦港獨狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />家陣中国製造好失禮你依條港燦？"},{"pid":"e589b2184facc5ce4ce266d78e5b128d0ab91c63","tid":2155581,"uid":165881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:20:50.000Z","msg":"中國將香港權益說成中國恩賜，一方面口說支持一國兩制，但行動就侵害香港在一國兩制的權利。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f396dca04008a6482942a23daa1e450a2aad9772","tid":2155581,"uid":291750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f80a107a29528441ca7898f379f9e9e6d60bc743","tid":2155581,"uid":99805,"like":103,"dislike":1,"score":102,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T01:44:48.000Z","msg":"只准政府9up<br />\n不准百姓討論？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:21:04.000Z","msg":"講明，你將觸犯國安法"},{"pid":"3dba718993c82a411aa324d49892f134b